The '''''Christian Examiner''''' is an online [[Christian]] [[newspaper|news site]]. Prior to July 1, 2014, it was a tabloid newspaper, published by Selah Media Group serving Southern California, Western Washington and the [[Minneapolis–Saint Paul]] metropolitan area of Minnesota. In early 2014, the newspaper ceased publishing and in July 2014 the trademark, URLs and website were sold to the Christian Media Corporation (CMC Group).{{cn||date=May 2018}}
